{"tid":730733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖情人拍裸照性侵　竟辯「她要我幫忙檢查菜花」","createTime":"2018-07-05T15:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T08:18:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"974f13116cef7cdf982b9640dd7d239fd6cc3a45","tid":730733,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:42:58.000Z","msg":"新北市陳姓男子和去年和女友因故分手後，竟持剪刀恐嚇她脫去衣褲，用手機拍裸照及私密處特寫再性侵，女子逃離後驗傷報警，陳男竟辯稱「是她要我幫忙看她有沒有長菜花」，但檢方不採信，依強制性交等罪將陳男起訴，士林地院今判這名恐怖情人3年6月及7月有期徒刑。<br />\n判決指出，陳男和被害人原本同居，最後因故分手。去年4月間陳男突然到前女友工作的卡拉OK店消費，等前女友下班後，老闆娘開車載送陳男和前女友返家途中，陳男要求老闆娘在沙崙海水浴場停車，然後拉著前女友到一處鐵皮屋，持剪刀恐嚇前女友脫去衣褲，「若不自己脫，要用剪刀刺」。<br />\n女方擔心遭遇不測，被迫脫光衣服，陳男隨即拿手機拍攝裸照和私密處特寫，再性侵得逞。事後被害人在友人陪同下驗傷報警。<br />\n陳男得知前女友報警後，竟將裸照傳給前女友，還恐嚇她「我傳Facebook給妳兒子看，看我敢不敢」。<br />\n陳男到案辯稱，當時2人確實有發生爭執，他持剪刀時，在拉扯過程中劃傷前女友手指，但宣稱拍攝裸照「是因為她想看自己生殖器有沒有長菜花，自願讓我拍攝裸照及私密處，且她的手指受傷流血，這種情況下，我怎麼可能跟她發生性關係」。<br />\n士林地院勘驗照片，發現受害女彎曲膝蓋、雙手置放在膝蓋前想遮擋胸部，顯見其並非出於自願拍攝裸照，且若女方想看下體是否有菜花，可以用手機開啟自拍模式，即可自行察看，無須他人協助拍攝，因此不採信陳男辯詞，今依強制性交罪判他3年6月徒刑，另依強制、恐嚇罪判刑7個月。仍可上訴。（顏凡裴／台北報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/234243_da30cabc4c24186877c0de89813c7771.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F234243_da30cabc4c24186877c0de89813c7771.png&h=d106b711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180704/1385212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180704%2F1385212&d=EIiSpltKyPuFfEZK1%2BieMgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2f70aa24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180704%2F1385212&h=aa262f72\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180704/1385212</a>"},{"pid":"2250b6aea04377cf593c0d66ae7385ac03199250","tid":730733,"uid":178619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:20:41.000Z","msg":"新北市又嬴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7495fa30a4198999284f6b1891ef764164a3a50e","tid":730733,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:14:23.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"2a80b8650983fe058b1b65c8fa055d5c3823635f","tid":730733,"uid":110969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:16:48.000Z","msg":"新北+1"},{"pid":"85808eeab5d3d1d8db64e4e7d724ee1ad2211acb","tid":730733,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:21:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新北Goal!</span></strong>"},{"pid":"821451dfab0ea67330a3381ce7d4e23c32036cb4","tid":730733,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:38:02.000Z","msg":"菜花圖呢"},{"pid":"745319f87b831194b5b0e0036158631d388e834e","tid":730733,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:44:55.000Z","msg":"台灣最美的是人"},{"pid":"b01c46ffea374fcb86eb2a04fe55ae18c64f1e50","tid":730733,"uid":8748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:46:46.000Z","msg":"所以話"},{"pid":"6a20f3c6e4832bcc8402e07b1805ca7c6a542f60","tid":730733,"uid":179938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"821451dfab0ea67330a3381ce7d4e23c32036cb4","tid":730733,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:38:02.000Z","msg":"菜花圖呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T01:16:19.000Z","msg":"尖銳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622a89afaf7520caba4847d424604b90d91773d1","tid":730733,"uid":145744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T01:21:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4071449e7ee9e733783adbd631cc309271833d9","tid":730733,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b01c46ffea374fcb86eb2a04fe55ae18c64f1e50","tid":730733,"uid":8748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:46:46.000Z","msg":"所以話